Extending Classes
-----------------
Example:
--------
Base or Parent class
--------------------
class Super 
{
    public:
      Super(); 
      void someMethod();
    protected: 
      int mProtectedInt;
    private:
      int mPrivateInt;
};

To build a new class called 'Sub' which inherit from 'Super' we use below syntax:

Inherited class
---------------
class Sub : public Super
{
    public
      Sub();
      void someOtherMethod();
}
